data.description: Located with close proximity to the Naval Weapons Station. This spacious 3 Bedroom and 3 Bathroom unit is ready for a new owner. The living room features vaulted ceilings and a wood burning fire place.  The screened balcony is great for a coffee overlooking the pond behind. There is a separate balcony for the primary bedroom. All appliances will convey with an acceptable offer.
